<ul><li><b>Reliant on the server</b>&nbsp;- if the server goes down the terminals lose functionality.<br></li><li>Requires a very&nbsp;<b>powerful and reliable server</b>&nbsp;which is expensive.</li><li>Server demand and&nbsp;<b>bandwidth</b>&nbsp;is increased.</li><li><b>Maintaining network connections </b>for portable devices&nbsp;<b>consumes more power</b>&nbsp;than local data processing.</li></ul>